data.title: 'Ethereum devs announce final date for Fusaka upgrade introducing PeerDAS in early December, a big move for the platform.'
data.description: In early December, Fusaka is set to launch a new data-sampling method for transactions known as PeerDAS. This innovative system aims to enhance efficiency in data processing for transactions. Stay tuned for the upcoming debut of Fusaka and its groundbreaking technology.

data.title: Global Revenue Cycle Management market to grow at 45.95% CAGR, exceeding USD 28560 billion by 2035 from USD 449.83 billion in 2024.
data.description: In New York as of October 30, 2025, it has been reported that the projected Global Revenue Cycle Management (RCM) Market is set to experience significant growth. Starting at USD 449.83 billion in 2024, the market is anticipated to reach a value of USD 28560 billion by 2035. This represents a remarkable Compound Annual Growth Rate (CAGR) of 45.95% throughout the forecast period. This substantial increase in value highlights the substantial potential for development in this industry.

data.title: Beneficient is back in compliance with Nasdaq's periodic filing and market value requirements.
data.description: Beneficient has successfully met Nasdaq's filing requirement and demonstrated a compliance with the market value of listed securities. This development signifies the company's adherence to Nasdaq regulations. The achievement is significant for Beneficient as it ensures continued listing on the exchange, safeguarding investor confidence. This compliance reflects positively on the company's financial health and stability. The successful compliance encompasses meeting specific criteria related to financial filings and market value of securities, which are crucial for maintaining a presence on Nasdaq.

data.title: Atypical Teratoid/Rhabdoid Tumor market sees promising growth with CAGR during 2025-2034, driven by rising molecular diagnosis & new therapies. Expanding pool of identified patients due to increased awareness.
data.description: The market for atypical teratoid/rhabdoid tumor is experiencing growth due to a surge in molecular diagnosis and higher awareness of this aggressive pediatric CNS cancer. This has led to an increase in the number of identified patients. Furthermore, the introduction of new therapies like PD-1 inhibitor is contributing to the market expansion.

data.title: Salvation Army emphasizes need to preserve SNAP benefits for 42 million Americans amid government shutdown and rising costs.
data.description: In Alexandria, Virginia on October 30, 2025, a significant portion of the American population is experiencing a lack of clarity regarding the Supplemental Nutrition Assistance Program (SNAP) due to an ongoing government shutdown and escalating expenses. With tens of millions of citizens affected, families are increasingly relying on food pantries for support amidst this crisis.

data.title: Nine Energy Service reveals Q3 2025 stats.
data.description: Last week, a new study reported that the global economy is projected to grow by 5.6% in 2021, which is higher than the previous estimate of 4.4%. The research also showed that international trade volume is forecasted to increase by 8.4% this year, compared to the earlier estimation of 7.2%. Furthermore, the study indicated that inflation rates are anticipated to reach 3.8% in advanced economies and 4.3% in emerging markets. This optimistic economic outlook is thought to be primarily driven by the rapid growth in the service sector, improved vaccine distribution, and stronger-than-expected recoveries in various countries.

data.title: Cerberus ODC and NVIDIA launch AI-RAN stack for AI-native 5G, moving towards 6G. Breakthrough in distributed AI inference at forward edge, NY, Oct. 30, 2025.
data.description: Cutting-edge software-defined architecture has recently achieved significant performance improvements, enabling distributed AI inference at the forward edge while also driving AI advancements for real-world applications. The Open RAN Development Company (ODC), backed by Cerberus Capital Management, announced this groundbreaking development on October 30, 2025. The innovative approach has led to a remarkable boost in capabilities, paving the way for further advancements in artificial intelligence.

data.title: Save Mart launches "Right By You" with $120K food bank match, holiday meals < $6, military discounts.958 stores in CA/NV.
data.description: A regional grocer based in Modesto, California has announced a 12-point plan to address increasing expenses in communities throughout California and Nevada. The Save Mart Companies, which oversees 191 stores under various brands, including Save Mart, Lucky, and FoodMaxx, introduced the initiative on October 30, 2025. This plan aims to tackle the challenges posed by escalating costs in the region.

data.title: Gran Tierra Energy Inc. posted Q3 results, with exploration success in Ecuador. Financials and operations discussed in USD.
data.description: Gran Tierra Energy Inc. disclosed its financial and operational results for the quarter ending on September 30, 2025. The numbers were reported in United States dollars, with production volumes being provided on an average working interest before royalties basis. The company operates under the tickers NYSE American: GTE, TSX: GTE, and LSE: GTE. Production is measured in barrels of oil equivalent per day (boepd or boe/d), based on WI sales before royalties. For a detailed breakdown of per barrel amounts based on net after royalty production, interested parties can refer to Gran Tierra's Quarterly Report on Form 10-Q filed on October 30, 2025.

data.title: CFAS is launched with 40+ leaders to operationalize AI in national security, incl. NVIDIA, Google, OpenAI, AWS.
data.description: Over 40 prominent figures from government, industry, and academia, including NVIDIA, Google, OpenAI, and AWS, gathered at the launch of the Center for Frontier AI Security in Arlington, Virginia on October 30, 2025. This initiative aims to translate policy into practical strategies for leveraging AI in enhancing national security measures. This collaboration signifies a significant step towards bridging the gap between theoretical frameworks and real-world applications in the field of AI security.

data.title: Netflix (NASDAQ: NFLX) to undergo 10-for-1 stock split; shares surge in extended trading. Nov. 10, 2025 record date set.
data.description: Netflix Inc. saw a rise in its shares during Thursday's after-hours trading following the announcement of a 10-to-1 forward stock split. The company's stock, listed as NFLX on the NASDAQ, experienced an increase. The split will grant each shareholder as of November 10, 2025, with the adjusted number of shares. data.title: NextDecade gives update on Q3-Q4 2025: finalized financing, achieved positive FIDs for Train 4 & Train 5.
data.description: Houston-based NextDecade Corporation announced their latest updates for the third quarter 2025 and early fourth quarter 2025. The company, listed as NEXT on the NASDAQ, shared significant milestones including successful financing and Final Investment Decisions (FIDs) for Rio Grande LNG Train 4 and Train 5. CEO Matt Schatzman expressed optimism, stating that these recent developments have been transformative for NextDecade by ensuring financial progress while avoiding dilution to company shares.
